oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Stones River Bridge collapsed
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of the collapsed Stones River Bridge, located on Highway 70S. People are gathered on the remaining parts of the bridge. A wagon is overturned in river.
